{% comment %}
  snippets/header-promo.liquid
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  ROW 1: Promo bar — navy background, message text, live countdown timer.

  VARIABLES (passed in via `with` from sections/header.liquid):
    promo_text    {string}  — the promotional message, e.g. "🛎️ Hurry! Sale ends in..."
    sale_end_time {string}  — ISO 8601 end date, e.g. "2025-12-31T23:59:59"
                              read by header.js to drive the countdown.

  DOES NOT READ:
    section.settings — all values are passed in; snippet is section-agnostic.

  CALLER (sections/header.liquid):
    {% if section.settings.show_promo %}
      {% render 'header-promo',
         promo_text:    section.settings.promo_text,
         sale_end_time: section.settings.sale_end_time
      %}
    {% endif %}

  NOTE: The {% if show_promo %} guard lives in the caller, not here.
  That keeps this snippet unconditional and independently testable.
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
{% endcomment %}

<div class="header__promo">
  <div class="header__promo-inner page-width">

    <span class="header__promo-text">
      {{- promo_text | escape -}}
    </span>

    {% comment %}
      data-end-time is the handoff point to header.js.
      The JS reads this attribute, calculates remaining seconds from now,
      and ticks the four unit spans down every second.
      Initial values (00D / 00H / 00M / 00S) are placeholders — JS overwrites
      them on the first tick, so there is no visible flash.
    {% endcomment %}
    <span
      class="header__promo-timer"
      data-end-time="{{ sale_end_time | escape }}"
      aria-live="polite"
      aria-label="Sale countdown timer"
    >
      <span class="header__promo-timer-unit" aria-hidden="true">00D</span>
      <span class="header__promo-timer-sep"  aria-hidden="true">:</span>
      <span class="header__promo-timer-unit" aria-hidden="true">00H</span>
      <span class="header__promo-timer-sep"  aria-hidden="true">:</span>
      <span class="header__promo-timer-unit" aria-hidden="true">00M</span>
      <span class="header__promo-timer-sep"  aria-hidden="true">:</span>
      <span class="header__promo-timer-unit" aria-hidden="true">00S</span>
    </span>

  </div>
</div>
